pan class="_ _6"></span>但实际上，<span class="_ _6"></span>有些人</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y42 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">对自身的问题一无所知，这也比动物好不了多少。比如说，</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y43 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">本来<span class="_ _d"></span>“我”<span class="_ _d"></span>不存在，<span class="_ _d"></span>你反而去执著<span class="_ _d"></span>“我”<span class="_ _d"></span>——这一点，<span class="_ _d"></span>没有</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y7a ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">学过空性的人，<span class="_ _d"></span>或许无法理解：<span class="_ _e"></span>“怎么会没有‘我’<span class="_ _6"></span>？<span class="_ _d"></span>‘我’</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y7b ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls3d ws0">不就在这儿吗！<span class="_ _8"></span><span class="ls3c">”但佛教里专门有一种观察方法，剖析所谓</span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y5a ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls14 ws0">的“我”在何处，这样观察下来，<span class="_ _8"></span><span class="ls12">“我”的确是了不可得。</span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y5b ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">这对有些同学来讲，<span class="_ _5"></span>可能是一个新知识，<span class="_ _5"></span>但我特别希望你们</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y5c ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">能种下<span class="_ _6"></span>“空性”<span class="_ _d"></span>的种子，<span class="_ _6"></span>以后善根成熟时，<span class="_ _d"></span>就很容易通达这</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y5d ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">个真理。</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
